b0c3a98cccf2e5b55719eabc","tid":309343,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>從來冇見過有男仔做診所護士，咁算唔算性別歧視？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：psy nursing rn fresh grad 冇offer想搵工做住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\npsy nurse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年dse唔夠高分，冇得揀之下入咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去老人院做啦</blockquote><br />\n講真我唔太想做院舍，因為聽啲阿sir講過話你RNP入到去一定係做最大嗰個，好多時第一日返工已經要做ic<br />\n試過有師兄就係咁嘅情況，仲要唔好彩第一日就有院友arrest咗要急救，喺都未熟悉個運作之下搓完人仲要做返晒所有document，最慘係冇人幫到你，唔通叫啲呀姐做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我諗住長遠一係等入返HA，一係寧願做政府工算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搓人同寫document好小野姐<br />\n<br />\nHA真係機會渺茫</blockquote><br />\n其實我出psy placement嗰陣啲rn都同我講話男仔HA請嘅機會都幾大，因為前線真係唔夠人同埋都走咗都唔止十個男rn，係唔知點解男嘅in完都請唔晒(唔止我一個no offer)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n院舍嚟講我自己就覺得係壓力大過醫院，自問仲未有能力可以做到獨當一面，同埋新嘢上手比較慢，始終喺醫院有其他rn/apn旁住會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fce03356d1ea16c0235a1cef92646eded269eeb","tid":309343,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>診所護士人工好低炸喎 又唔洗degree<br />\n你psy rn唔洗揀呢份工啦</blockquote><br />\n諗住等攞到個牌之前搵啲part-time做下先，依家未有牌就算院舍工都申請唔到<br />\n好似八月先攞到個牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17a4db199feacd2d129058af79f48f2494d070e","tid":309343,"uid":13841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譚仔店面都好似無見